{"data":[{"id":564558198,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c53a6bf084174c465b43f4246b7493fd","url_token":"Wayne.Ye","name":"WayneYe","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/a08141a5a4a8efd637722a8ae207f770_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/a08141a5a4a8efd637722a8ae207f770_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c53a6bf084174c465b43f4246b7493fd","user_type":"people","headline":"普通的大学生","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564558198","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546395751,"updated_time":1546395751,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e  1号凌晨一个朋友把这个证明发给我看，那时候其实看完第一页就和朋友说了两个逻辑推理有错误，看了下这个问题底下很多大佬基本把错误都详细说了，就不谈了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  我想说的一点不是证明错误的地方，而是其实他的证明书写方式。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  用正规的逻辑推理的数学语言，最多一张纸就完完整整的写完了，也就是析取合取、与或非的那些公式，不太了解的朋友可以百度看一看，应该中学也有接触过一些。如果有心去证明这样一个大定理，理应严谨的使用数学工具，实际上逻辑证明的工具也不是很高端的东西，任何一本《离散数学》教材一般都在一二章作为基础知识，对于高中生来说也是很容易学习的，白话式的证明我只能用一个词“拙劣”来形容。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  拙劣的证明公开发布，受到更专业的人士嘲笑是很正常的事。我赞同证明者的勇气，但不赞同方式。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  正因为对待“数学”的态度不同，所以一部分为了达到数学殿堂宝座而锲而不舍的学习更高更深知识的人，成为了数学家。他们可以为了表达一个看起来确实很显然的定理不厌其烦的写一大段证明，用天衣无缝的逻辑让你无从攻破。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  而另一部分人同样为了达到这个目标，却只想着用已掌握的初等或是高等数学知识，用最模棱两可的大白话去攀登数学的高峰。他们想挑战，却不去钻研数学家是如何证明的，更不会去花时间学习更深入更难的知识。用一句话形容最恰当不过，叫无知者无畏。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  学习数学，证明数学，成为数学，在数学上一切业余和专业的差别其实没有多少，只差两个字，数学家却因有它而伟大，数也因它而成为“学”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  它叫\u003cb\u003e“严谨”\u003c/b\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"1号凌晨一个朋友把这个证明发给我看，那时候其实看完第一页就和朋友说了两个逻辑推理有错误，看了下这个问题底下很多大佬基本把错误都详细说了，就不谈了。 我想说的一点不是证明错误的地方，而是其实他的证明书写方式。 用正规的逻辑推理的数学语言，最多…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=220\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion